Hello Curt,

Tuesday, November 24, 1998, you wrote:
CE> Second, I often see people combining several flag values into one hex number
CE> in their code.  I prefer to use the flags individually, separated by the
CE> "|", as it makes it easier for me later to see and change the flags I have
