your email not very uplifting to say the least. And it certainly doesnt
encourage me to buy any software from you, looking at the way u seem to
react.

Shit happens, if one is truely convinced of what she/he does and what ones
capabillities are, would there then be any need to start defending 
oneself?

-- 
