Well we've had much bigger archives posted to the list recently
so here it comes. As usual with my work the functions were
created for my own project but they were written in a modular
way which means they can be included and used with very little
work in any other project. Features are a bit limited but I hope
to expand the poer soon as I upgrade the AHI support in my
own project.

sorry the source isn't in ascii format but as far as I know there are
no non-standard libs used in th code appart from the supplied
ahi lib so problems are minimal.

Cheers,

-- 
< Paul Burkey - http://www.sneech.demon.co.uk >

