          Paris Thu, 5 Nov 1998 22:40:45 +0100 (MET)
          Paris Thu, 5 Nov 1998 22:40:42 +0100 (MET)
From: Vincent Demongodin <v.demongodin@wanadoo.fr>
Date: Fri, 06 Nov 1998 06:05:28 -0500
Subject: Re: Busy Pointers!!!

Use that:

With amigalibs.res as residentfor TagItem structure:


Statement BusyPointer{numWindow.b}

  Dim p.TagItem(2)

  p(1)\ti_Tag=#WA_BusyPointer,True
  p(2)\ti_Tag=#TAG_DONE,0

  SetWindowPointerA_ Peek.l(Addr Window(numWindow)),&p(1)

End Statement




Statement NormalPointer{numWindow.b}

  Dim p.TagItem(2)

  p(1)\ti_Tag=#WA_Pointer,0
  p(2)\ti_Tag=#TAG_DONE,0

  SetWindowPointerA_ Peek.l(Addr Window(numWindow)),&p(1)

End Statement


Ciao!
Vincent.



-- 
Vincent Demongodin
