Subject: Re: GTListViews

On 5 Nov 98, at 11:26, Wright J.A wrote:

> hi ppl,
>           ok all i got a nice GTListview all working nicley BUT i want t=
o
> make it so that when the user scrolls with the scrollbar it responds
> immediately instead of updateing when you release it. So how`d you do it=
?

You need to do this before(?) opening your window. Or maybe after. 
But try before first. You'll also want to use amigalibs.res.

AddIDCMP #IDCMP_INTUITICKS | #IDCMP_MOUSEMOVE | #IDCMP_GADGETDOWN

 
