Cop$+mki$($ec)+mki$(START.l+120)	;BPL4PTH

Initcoplist 0,44,160,3,8,16,-6
Displayuser 0,0,Cop$

Vwait 50
Blitz
Createdisplay 0
Mousewait
end
...
This ain't working but I can't see why... Please, help:-(

Sasu Lintula


