> 
> I don't think it's likely to be possible to do blits any faster than
> the routines that blitz already offers when using the hardware
> blitter.

BB2 is stopping your code while blitting. This is annoying. That could
be overcome by installing a blitter interrupt. This would speed up
thing dramatically. The only way to blit faster is using interleaved 
bitplanes because you dont need to setup your blitter after every plane.

