Subject: I solved the "real" problem: Bug in EFMUILib

Warning: This is a message in MIME format. Your mail reader does not
support MIME. Some parts of this message will be readable as plain text.
To see the rest, you will need to upgrade your mail reader.


--BOUNDARY.1749136240.3

Hi all!

The problem that I complained yesterday on the list is caused by EFMUI Lib.

If you open more than 14 mui window objects your application will crash
sooner
or later. 

I attach some source to this mail. You can run it as many times as you like
it. It won`t
crash. But if you then uncomment the two lines which open the 15th window,
it`ll
crash after two or three compiles. It would be very kind of you if anyone
could test
this -- because the problem is still a strange one and I want to know if
it`s only on
my amiga.

I`ll also inform the author of EFMuilib. 

-- 
Greetings,

           Andreas

