 for blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie; Wed, 25 Nov 1998 00:16:26 +0000
From: "Paul" <paulwest@stationone.demon.co.uk>
Organization: private
Date: 25 Nov 98 00:08:02 +0000
Subject: Mildred library

