@NODE "Mail_305" "Re: Mouse Positions in Amiga Mode"
 for blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie; Thu, 5 Nov 1998 19:13:47 +0000
From: Paul Burkey <burkey@bigfoot.com>
Date: Thu, 05 Nov 1998 20:04:09 +0000
Subject: Re: Mouse Positions in Amiga Mode

Hi,

> Does anyone know how to read the mouse position in Amiga mode. (I'm
looking
> for something list tye MouseX and MouseY commands used in Blitz mode). 

SMouseX and SMouseY can be used in a similar way to MouseX and
MouseY but you can also use EMouseX an EMouseY for checking the
coordinates of the mouse on the last Event eg, the last Mouse Click.

Cheers,

