--BOUNDARY.1748829936.2
Encoding: quoted-printable


    Hello Blitzers,

    Here is the new version of the NCS, so try to look at it just to see
what it can be achieve with these commands :).

    Previous problems (Resident clashs, libs numbers which are already
assigned) should be solved forever. Here is a quick description of new
functions:
    + Lightning fast IFF/ILBM loader/decoder
    + Friendly 'Blit' function
    + New 2D Drawing system (can be output on Window, BitMap or even
directly on Screen !), with some interresting functions (NCopyBitmap(),..=
=2E.)
    + New Bitmap library to have full bitmap support in an OS clean way
    + Window/Screen command syntax changed (easier)
    + Most of the libraries have been optimized
    + New locale support (with catalog support)
    + All guide files have been updated..
    + OS Double buffering function ! (fast). Works with Rom 2.0 too. =

    + Some little changes,

        Happy testing and coding. If you find any bugs, mail me! I'm stil=
l
developping this package, so if you want a bug free pack, report bugs :-)=


        Regards,

                        Fred.

