Date: Mon, 23 Nov 1998 01:29:22 +0000
Subject: Resident Clashing

Hi all,

I'm trying to write an mui app that uses AHI sounds. Therefore I'm using
Paul Burkey's AHI routines (which strangely don't work anymore, but did the
other day), and EFMUI lib. The residents look like this :

    blitzlibs:amigalibs.res
    blitzlibs:bb2objtypes.res
    blitzlibs:mui.res

But when I click OK on the CompilerOption I get a clash in the resident
files. Is there anyway around this, as I can't have AHI with MUI t the
minute.

-- 
Cheers,
