None that I could find... if I'm after some commands, I usually just load=
 the
deflibs file or the main blitz2 executable into HEX and search for keywor=
ds

This is all I've found to do with serial I/O:

OpenSerial
WriteSerial
WriteSerialString
ReadSerial
ReadSerialString
CloseSerial
SetSerialBuffer
SetSerialLens
SerialEvent

I hope that helps a little...

