There is a listing of the commands in the RIStoncracker.lib doc.  Also
should be some examples from RWE.  To use them, you also need the
RIstonecracker.lib.  I have these, but I don't know if it came with Blitz
or with the BSS only.

Look in your Blitzlibs: directories for the library.  If it's in there, you
should also find the examples and doc somewhere in your Blitz setup (or
maybe still on your Blitz disks.)  If you don't have it, you might try
getting the RiBlitzlibs
 file that's in Aminet/dev/basic/   I'm not sure if it's there or not, maybe
someone else knows?

