@NODE "Mail_592" "To use Deflibs or not to use Deflibs..."
 for blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie; Sat, 21 Nov 1998 22:42:16 +0000
From: James L Boyd <jamesboyd@velvety.demon.co.uk>
Date: Sat, 21 Nov 1998 22:37:17 +0000
Subject: To use Deflibs or not to use Deflibs...

Hi all,

Somebody mentioned getting rid of deflibs as it's not needed and
Blitz would use the installed libs automatically...

I've just tried renaming deflibs and running Blitz, and it doesn't
use any of the libs in my Blitzlibs: setup...

What's the deal here?

See ya,

-- 
